When writing, reviewing, or fixing Playwright E2E tests for this project, follow the conventions in @.claude/skills/playwright/SKILL.md.

To run tests:
```bash
./scripts/test-e2e.sh --quiet <file> [--grep "\"<pattern>\""]
```
